<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="H" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Hallo" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Hallo,</orth> or <orth extent="full" opt="n">Halloo</orth> (M. Edd.) or <orth extent="full" opt="n">Hallow</orth> (O. Edd.) to cry out, to call or shout to with a loud voice: <bibl n="shak. tgv 5.4.13" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. V, 4, 13</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 3.3.78" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. III, 3, 78</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 1.2.213" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B I, 2, 213</bibl>. Trans.: <cit><quote>--ing your name to the reverberate hills,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tn 1.5.291" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. I, 5, 291</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>